Name: Parkour
About the game: Parkour is a runner game with tons of challenges. Your objective is simple - try to run as far as possible. The levels are randomly generated. The difficulty increases as you run farther. Lava, monsters, powerups & your quick 'decision making' will change your fate. Features : - Randomly generated chunks - Powerups (speed, points, invincibility, health) - Various obstacles (lava, spikes, monsters) - Different levels can be explored as you run farther - Achievements & leaderboard (Google Play, Steam)
